	Claude Heiland-Allen is 17, likes strange music, stranger maths
	and the strangest programming. Despite this, he still finds time
	to go out and have large amounts of fun, often by confusing
	innocent bystanders with the power of strange music, some of which
	is the fruit of his own twisted imagination.

@endnode

